Distractor analysis:
- A: [Partial Scope] [Structural Inversion] Reverses the actual sequence of ideas the passage develops.
- C: [Narrative Speculation] [Partial Scope] Describes only part of the passage, ignoring its overall trajectory.
- D: [Structural Inversion] [Narrative Speculation] Imports unsupported assumptions about author motivation or future plans.', NULL, 'Craft and Structure', 'Text Structure and Purpose', 'reading_writing', 'craft', 'TSP', NULL, 'hard', false, 'SAT', 'multiple_choice', true, true, 'scholaris_ai', '{"dsat_blueprint_v1":true,"rw_subtype":"structure","rw_format":"passage_mc","generator":"regenerate-english-fresh.mjs","regen_seed_offset":100000,"explanation_v2":true}'::jsonb, now(), now());
