out accounting for the theoretical setup and evidentiary middle the passage develops before reaching that recommendation here throughout.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Narrative Speculation] [Partial Scope] Describes only part of the passage, ignoring its overall trajectory."},{"id":"D","text":"It attributes personal ambition to the author instead of analyzing how the text moves from observation to qualified generalization across successive sentences throughout overall in sum, rather than","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Structural Inversion] [Narrative Speculation] Imports unsupported assumptions about author motivation or future plans."}]'::jsonb, 'B', 'Step 1 — Identify the passage organization
