aim, supplies seasonal field evidence, and acknowledges limitations before drawing implications throughout overall in sum in context as written here throughout overall as written here throughout","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Correct (C). Correct (C). This choice matches the passage''s rhetorical architecture from framework through evidence to qualified implications."},{"id":"D","text":"It lists technical vocabulary from the opening sentences without showing how those terms support a cumulative argument across the full paragraph from mechanism to outcome overall, as the passage''s own framing here throughout overall.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Structural Inversion] [Partial Scope] Describes only part of the passage, ignoring its overall trajectory."}]'::jsonb, 'C', 'Step 1 — Identify the passage organization
