hed model to challenge overall in sum.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Structural Inversion] Reverses the actual sequence of ideas the passage develops."},{"id":"D","text":"It contrasts an earlier consensus with newer findings, reconciles partial agreement with dispute, and qualifies the scope of the conclusion in sum in context as written.","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Correct (D). Correct (D). This choice matches the passage''s rhetorical architecture from framework through evidence to qualified implications."}]'::jsonb, 'D', 'Step 1 — Identify the passage organization
